AWS Systemts Manger-SSM
=======================
1) Run Command and State Manager   - Deploy Configure and Administer
2) Maintenance Window and Parameter Store - Shared Capabilities
3) Inverntory , Patch Manager, Automation - Track and Update

Advantages of SSM
==================
1) Supports for hybrid architecture
2) cross-platfrom
3) Scalable
4) Secure
5) Easy to Write automation
6) Expected Reduction in Total Cost of Ownership (TCO)

